<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; }
        .header { text-align: center; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 2px solid #10b981; }
        .content { padding: 20px 0; }
        .footer { font-size: 12px; text-align: center; color: #718096; margin-top: 20px; }
        .salary { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #059669; }
        .details { background: #f0fdf4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Payroll Generated</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Your payroll for <strong>{{month}}/{{year}}</strong> has been generated successfully.</p>
            
            <div class="details">
                <p>Net Salary Disbursed:</p>
                <p class="salary">₹{{salary}}</p>
                <p>Status: <span style="color: #6366f1; font-weight: bold;">Processed</span></p>
            </div>
            
            <p>You can view and download your payslip from the employee dashboard.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for being part of our team!</p>
            <p>© CRM System</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
